fields.value: Pre-processed brain structural images and the psychological data of parental attitude towards praising children

dsDescriptionValue.value:
There are 225 brain structural images that includes the information of regional gray matter volume of children and adolescents (mean age : 5-18). In addition, we share the behavioral data of parental attitude towards praising their children, personality traits of children, and some characteristics of participants of the present study.
More details of the design of our project and the way of acquisition and processing of imaging data were described in Taki et al. (2010) http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21170334.
